pos_sum=0
neg_sum=0
pos_count=0
neg_count=0
while True:
    num=int(input("enter the number(-1 to stop):"))
    if num==-1:
        break
    if num>0:
        pos_sum+=num
        pos_count+=1
    elif num<0:
        neg_sum+=num
        neg_count+=1
    #calculate averages
    if pos_count>0:
        pos_avg=pos_sum/pos_count
    else:
        pos_avg=0
    if neg_count>0:
        neg_avg=neg_sum/neg_count
    else:
        neg_avg=0
    #display results
    print("Average of positive numbers:",pos_avg)
    print("Average of negative numbers:",neg_avg)

output
enter the number(-1 to stop):Average of positive numbers: 9.0
Average of negative numbers: 0
enter the number(-1 to stop):Average of positive numbers: 7.0
Average of negative numbers: 0
enter the number(-1 to stop):Average of positive numbers: 7.0
Average of negative numbers: -8.0
enter the number(-1 to stop):Average of positive numbers: 7.0
Average of negative numbers: -8.5
Average of positive numbers: 6.666666666666667
Average of negative numbers: -8.5
